title: Save Typeform survey results to Airtable
description: With this workflow, you can collect the data from Typeform with the Typeform Trigger node every time someone submits a response and save it to Airtable with the Airtable node.
disclaimer: This workflow is provided as-is. Please review and test before using in production.
